Name: Mahjong Dimensions 3D - Fantasy Anime
About the game: Mahjong Dimensions 3D - Fantasy Anime is the game where you have to solve the problems as fast as possible. You have to find the two similar tales that match. Mahjong Dimensions 3D - Fantasy Anime become one of the most popular free board game all over the world. This is the innovative Mahjong Classic versions, where scenario is limited by time, so you have to beat the time and match tiles. Everything totally depends on time strategy and how your brain works. This Mahjong game is a classic board game type. This Mahjong journey will be very addictive and the game is for all ages to play, as it helps your brain to workout hard. There is a time limit for you, so be as fast as possible. It is all about speed and memory, this addictive game will check your skills. You’ll get bonus points for matching several of the same image types in a row. If you love puzzle, strategy, memory, and brain training challenges games like crossword, chess, Mahjong, word search, solitaire and patience, you’ll will love Mahjong Dimensions 3D.
